nodes.text: KOTOR Campaign Guide Web Enhancement 3: Elbee (T1-LB)

KOTOR Campaign Guide Web Enhancement 3: Elbee (T1-LB) is an online supplement for Star Wars Roleplaying Game. It was published on the Wizards of the Coast website on September 24, 2008 and is a thitd in the series of web enhancements, which present material that didn't made it into Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide because of space reasons. This article covers T1-LB from the Knights of the Old Republic comic series.
